# The error indicates that the insertion of coal into the furnace failed because there are no coal units left in my inventory. 
# Currently, my inventory shows:
# - 2 transport belts
# - 2 stone bricks
# - 8 stones
# - 10 iron ore
# - 5 copper ore
# - 1 copper plate
# - 4 copper cables
# - 1 iron gear wheel

# It appears that I have lost track of my coal supply. I need to gather more coal before I can smelt the iron ore.

# Let's find and move to the nearest coal resource to gather some.
move_to(nearest(Resource.Coal))  # Move towards the nearest coal resource location to harvest coal.
